                                             rdfs:comment "This vocabulary describes flash cards. A flash card contains information such as words, numbers or images. Flash cards are used by students in classroom drills or in private study to improve memorization. A card contains the information being memorized and is divided into a question and a related answer. Multiple related cards can be grouped in a stack."@en ;
